data.description: Charming 3 bedroom 2.5 bath house nestled on a serene wooded lot offering the perfect blend of comfort and privacy.  The home features a sunroom with a new rubber roof, a sun soaked retreat where you can enjoy the beauty of your private backyard year round.  Adding a touch of character throughout the home you'll find built in stained glass window features and a stone fireplace.  The large 12X24 shed provides added storage for a riding mower, tools or even a workshop and an additional garden shed is also located on the property.  Partially finished basement is a versatile space, ideal for hobbyists and craft enthusiasts, with endless possibilities for customization.  If you need a 4th bedroom, the den, complete with built ins and a closet is a definite possibility.
